{"tid":1812260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益-解散警隊需解決嘅實際問題","createTime":"2020-01-05T10:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T13:35:08.000Z","uid":26876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5fdf4ff0c0fab222833fbe71a8a005580ba55b7f","tid":1812260,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"1. 治安問題<br />\n有兩大方面，第一方面係無咗狗隊邊個幫手執法維持治安： 呢個之前已有解決方案，由其他紀律部隊借調人手，成立臨時治安官<br />\n<br />\n第二方面係市面上多咗3萬隻流浪狗暴徒：除咗處決曬佢地暫時未有方案<br />\n<br />\n2. 狗宿<br />\n點樣踢走狗隻及他們家人出狗宿<br />\n<br />\n3. 部份供樓狗隻會供唔到樓陷家產，令市場出現大量銀主盤<br />\n<br />\n4. 狗隻和他們家人反對聲音<br />\n一隻狗一家四口，最少有12萬人反對<br />\n未計自私舔共藍絲<br />\n<br />\n大家諗諗計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">振興黃色經濟 拒絕幫襯建制</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6wEt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6wEt9.jpg&h=75dfc14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avbtvJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavbtvJ0.jpg&h=e1c98503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊心祝福<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug7anh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug7anh2.png&h=2bf968e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb97773fa063b464c578b589c1768db97fc59ad0","tid":1812260,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"【警告】今個新年 屯門水貨客問題特別嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1812